data.description: Welcome to this stunning three-bedroom, two-bathroom home, a true gem built in 2022. Nestled on a tranquil 2.18-acre parcel of land, this property offers a perfect blend of modern design and natural serenity. Situated approximately 4 miles from I-75, you'll enjoy convenient access to major routes, making your daily commute a breeze.  Upon stepping inside, you'll be greeted by luxury vinyl flooring that spans throughout the entire home. The open floorplan seamlessly connects the kitchen, dining area, and living room, creating a spacious and inviting atmosphere for family gatherings and entertaining.  The kitchen features a central island with a breakfast bar, a corner pantry for all your storage needs, and a gas range for cooking versatility. The abundant natural light and sleek design make this kitchen a hub for both cooking and socializing.  What sets this property apart is its private location, offering peace and tranquility while still being close to many conveniences. Escape the hustle and bustle of city life, unwind in your own slice of paradise, and relish the amenities this home has to offer. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to make this property your dream home!
